nt_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>All good I’m hitting up friends, family, co workers, and ham radio operators between me and Middleton . Helps that I grew up in this area and know a ton of people out to this west direction.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1468442668852973668", "author": "bobb", "author_handle": "bbobbert", "user_id": "207870503778517002", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/207870503778517002/4d6967ec4c70b2f76e67e14d9af37171.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, February 3, 2026 10:06 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-03 10:06 p.m.", "text": "That would actually be a great spot", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>That would actually be a great spot</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1468452679570423838", "author": "Orum", "author_handle": "maynguene_banana", "user_id": "548366727663321098", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/548366727663321098/6210fc66816c4710965df8dcb36b1795.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, February 3, 2026 10:46 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-03 10:46 p.m.", "text": "I can already make it across Monona to iHateComputer's repeater at times.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I can already make it across Monona to iHateComputer&#39;s repeater at times.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1468453987446554778", "author": "bobb", "author_handle": "bbobbert", "user_id": "207870503778517002", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/207870503778517002/4d6967ec4c70b2f76e67e14d9af37171.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, February 3, 2026 10:51 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-03 10:51 p.m.", "text": "Monona seems well-covered", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Monona seems well-covered</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1468621083333623949", "author": "W1SCO", "author_handle": "madmodder1", "user_id": "209364725383954443", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/209364725383954443/2440cdd95d8134e1486dec2e119abfb2.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Wednesday, February 4, 2026 9:55 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-04 9:55 a.m.", "text": "I also have contact info for a couple cell tower maintenance techs that work in the area.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I also have contact info for a couple cell tower maintenance techs that work in the area.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=eyes><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👀 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f440.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>3</span></div><div class=chatlog__reaction title=fire><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=🔥 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f525.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1468724577310998728", "author": "W1SCO", "author_handle": "madmodder1", "user_id": "209364725383954443", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/209364725383954443/2440cdd95d8134e1486dec2e119abfb2.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Wednesday, February 4, 2026 4:47 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-04 4:47 p.m.", "text": "I work for a sister company that has internal teams and sharepoint combined. So easy to find some contacts to pick their brain about requirements. Tower Maint techs and RF Engineers, might know what requirements or best practices that are needed to get a repeater on a tower. Oh and we do have a tower at the driveway of the Pleasant View Golf Course in Middleton........hmmmmmm. Loing shot getting on the tower, but would be ideal.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I work for a sister company that has internal teams and sharepoint combined. So easy to find some contacts to pick their brain about requirements. Tower Maint techs and RF Engineers, might know what requirements or best practices that are needed to get a repeater on a tower. Oh and we do have a tower at the driveway of the Pleasant View Golf Course in Middleton........hmmmmmm. Loing shot getting on the tower, but would be ideal.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=fire><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=🔥 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f525.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1468786091803938929", "author": "bobb", "author_handle": "bbobbert", "user_id": "207870503778517002", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/207870503778517002/4d6967ec4c70b2f76e67e14d9af37171.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Wednesday, February 4, 2026 8:51 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-04 8:51 p.m.", "text": "PLEASE", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>PLEASE</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1468799305652506729", "author": "W1SCO", "author_handle": "madmodder1", "user_id": "209364725383