ention\" title=\"bbobbert\">@bobb</span> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/HZ4U4yDPs\">https://discord.gg/HZ4U4yDPs</a>\nhere&#39;s the Madison MC discord -- still pretty new</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1469017238563459263", "author": "W1SCO", "author_handle": "madmodder1", "user_id": "209364725383954443", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/209364725383954443/2440cdd95d8134e1486dec2e119abfb2.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, February 5, 2026 12:10 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-05 12:10 p.m.", "text": "Also there is the Meshconsin discord where there is 700 some people from all of Wisconsin, with a Madison channel and a meshcore channel", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Also there is the Meshconsin discord where there is 700 some people from all of Wisconsin, with a Madison channel and a meshcore channel</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=thumbsup><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👍 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f44d.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1476443236766584964", "author": "Aenigma", "author_handle": "lordofthisworld", "user_id": "513365537573699594", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/513365537573699594/c3a124d9aac75fb9a67319542527cd2a.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Wednesday, February 25, 2026 11:58 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-25 11:58 p.m.", "text": "Are Madison nodes using the default US preset (910.525MHz, SF7, BW62.5, CR5)? I’m in Ozaukee County and talking with folks about putting MC nodes up on repeater towers. I’d like to make sure we would be interoperable between Madison, Milwaukee, and other nearby counties.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Are Madison nodes using the default US preset (910.525MHz, SF7, BW62.5, CR5)? I’m in Ozaukee County and talking with folks about putting MC nodes up on repeater towers. I’d like to make sure we would be interoperable between Madison, Milwaukee, and other nearby counties.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1476446986965221479", "author": "Orum", "author_handle": "maynguene_banana", "user_id": "548366727663321098", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/548366727663321098/6210fc66816c4710965df8dcb36b1795.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, February 26, 2026 12:13 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-26 12:13 a.m.", "text": "Yeah, the standard US preset (which I think is sometimes called \"narrow\" in the app).", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Yeah, the standard US preset (which I think is sometimes called &quot;narrow&quot; in the app).</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=thumbsup_tone1><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👍🏻 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f44d-1f3fb.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1479310094859763905", "author": "bobb", "author_handle": "bbobbert", "user_id": "207870503778517002", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/207870503778517002/4d6967ec4c70b2f76e67e14d9af37171.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, March 5, 2026 9:50 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-03-05 9:50 p.m.", "text": "For future reference!! http://madmesh.net/", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\">